  <brief_title>A Personalised Percutaneous External 3D Guide for Scaphoid Fixation</brief_title>
  <acronym>Scaphix</acronym>
  <official_title>Analysis of a Customized Percutaneous External Guidance System for Scaphoid Fracture Fixation Using 3D Printing</official_title>
